<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Harpoon of the Depths</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/harpoon_of_the_depths.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/piercing.shtml">Piercing</a><BR>
Damage per second - 6.80<BR>
Damage 8 - Delay 25<BR>
Weight: 6.5 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/weapons/piercing.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/paladin/weapons/piercing.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/weapons/piercing.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/weapons/piercing.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/piercing.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/weapons/piercing.shtml">SHM</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
(DEX +2) (HP +20) </font>
<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 2365pp (36 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 1652pp (11 quotes)<BR>

