<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>We camped this item in the Lake of Ill Omen on several occasions. The first time I was there I saw one drop, two hours later another one dropped, (won the roll with a 22), then nothing for hours and hours on end...I tallied the kills and they amounted to over 120 dead bloodgills in about a six hour period. We returned here and there over the course of a few days, possibly another 5-6 hours all told and still nada. My friend sold one of his for 2k and I am keeping mine for a little while. I will admit, very difficult to aquire, since you mainly fight while underwater (Endur. Breath) or have a good puller out to the land, but that takes a bit longer between kills. Some may say Bah to the high prices that these yeild, to those I say go grab one, then try for two...</font></td></tr></table>
