<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Miladian</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-05 01:07:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This weapon does indeed still drop, in the Lake of Ill Omen. Picked one of these up tonight off a bloodgill Goblin. There was another group there that said they got 3 tonight so its rare, but random loot. The stats on this weapon are nearly the same as the Yak and the EBW (.32 vs. .333) and its got buffs to boot. <BR>
<BR>
The only problems with it are, its primary hand only and won't go in the range slot. It is usable by all melee classes plus shaman, strangely its also usable by paladins even though they get no skill in piercing.</font></td></tr></table>
